          h2.augmented-name 7 Questions to Ram Jakaria

          hr.augmented-line
          .augmented-chat-holder.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/talkpush.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter")
              .arrow.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-message.talkpush Hello please tell us about your scope of work responsibilities?
          .augmented-chat-holder.left
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/ram.jpeg", alt="Augmented Recruiter").left
              .arrow.left
            .augmented-chat-message I’m Ram and works as a Sourcing Specialist of [24]7 Customer Philippines.  I’m part of the Sourcing team and I screen applicants over the phone to validate if they have met the requirements needed for the job and I then invite them to our recruitment site to continue the recruitment process.

          hr.augmented-line
          .augmented-chat-holder.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/talkpush.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter")
              .arrow.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-message.talkpush What do you like most working in recruitment?
          .augmented-chat-holder.left
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/ram.jpeg", alt="Augmented Recruiter").left
              .arrow.left
            .augmented-chat-message It’s both exciting and rewarding. I get the opportunity to change someone’s life for the better which is a great feeling. I can play a massive part in making it happen.

          hr.augmented-line
          .augmented-chat-holder.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/talkpush.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter")
              .arrow.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-message.talkpush How has technology changed the way you work since you started out in recruitment?
          .augmented-chat-holder.left
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/ram.jpeg", alt="Augmented Recruiter").left
              .arrow.left
            .augmented-chat-message I have been part of the Sourcing team for the past 14 months and I have seen how technology converted our recruitment process from being manual to digital which means we could now do almost everything with just one click. We are no longer restricted to doing recruitment within a certain time and space, since we integrated social media in our sourcing, which means we’re essentially hiring 24/7.

          hr.augmented-line
          .augmented-chat-holder.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/talkpush.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter")
              .arrow.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-message.talkpush What is the future role of Artificial Intelligence in recruitment?
          .augmented-chat-holder.left
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/ram.jpeg", alt="Augmented Recruiter").left
              .arrow.left
            .augmented-chat-message I think AI in recruitment saves an awful lot of time, provides better candidate experiences, increases recruiter productivity and finally creates a great first impression with candidates, which reinforces our employer brand.

          hr.augmented-line
          .augmented-chat-holder.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/talkpush.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter")
              .arrow.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-message.talkpush What makes the recruitment process you have built different/unique?
          .augmented-chat-holder.left
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/ram.jpeg", alt="Augmented Recruiter").left
              .arrow.left
            .augmented-chat-message We invest on our candidate recruitment experience to attract high caliber applicants. Word of mouth can be very influential. We increase that by making sure we treat every candidate with equal respect regardless of whether they fit for the job or not. It is important to acknowledge their effort and the investment in time they made to apply to our company.

          hr.augmented-line
          .augmented-chat-holder.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/talkpush.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter")
              .arrow.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-message.talkpush Aside from Talkpush what are your other favourite tools/ platforms that you use will you recommend to your fellow augmented recruiters?
          .augmented-chat-holder.left
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/ram.jpeg", alt="Augmented Recruiter").left
              .arrow.left
            .augmented-chat-message Facebook!

          hr.augmented-line
          .augmented-chat-holder.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-display
              img(src="../images/augmented-page/talkpush.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter")
              .arrow.talkpush
            .augmented-chat-message.talkpush Enough about recruitment! What is your favourite science fiction movie of all time?
